==English==
=== Noun ===
'''fat-ass''' also '''fatass''' (''plural'' '''fat-asses''')
# (''pejorative'') A [[jibe]] used on someone disliked or regarded as [[lazy]]
#* My [[boss]] is a '''fat-ass''' who doesn't know his job as well as I do.
#* Yes, your whole department is full of '''fat-asses'''.
# (''coarse slang'') A insulting term to describe an obese person.
#* Bob is such a fat-ass he can barely put his feet together.